{"html":"<br/>\n<h2>Fact Symbols with Injective Instances</h2><br/>\n<p class=\"monospace rules\">None</p><br/>\n<h2>Multiset Rewriting Rules</h2><br/>\n<p class=\"monospace rules\"><span class=\"hl_keyword\">rule</span> (<span class=\"hl_keyword\">modulo</span> AC) isend:<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> !KU( x ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">--[</span> K( x ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]-&gt;</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> In( x ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_comment\">/* has exactly the trivial AC variant */</span><br/>\n<br/>\n<br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">rule</span> (<span class=\"hl_keyword\">modulo</span> AC) irecv:<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> Out( x ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">--&gt;</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> !KD( x ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_comment\">/* has exactly the trivial AC variant */</span><br/>\n<br/>\n<br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">rule</span> (<span class=\"hl_keyword\">modulo</span> E) Init[color=#ffffff, process=&quot;|&quot;,<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;issapicrule, role=&#39;Process&#39;]:<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">--[</span> Init( ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]-&gt;</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> State_( ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_comment\">/* has exactly the trivial AC variant */</span><br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">rule</span> (<span class=\"hl_keyword\">modulo</span> E) p_0_[color=#ffffff, process=&quot;|&quot;,<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;issapicrule, role=&#39;Process&#39;]:<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> State_( ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">--&gt;</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> State_1( ), State_2( ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_comment\">/* has exactly the trivial AC variant */</span><br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">rule</span> (<span class=\"hl_keyword\">modulo</span> E) newx_0_1[color=#ffffff,<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;process=&quot;new x.1;&quot;, issapicrule, role=&#39;Process&#39;]:<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> State_1( ), Fr( x.1 ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">--&gt;</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> State_11( x.1 ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_comment\">/*<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_keyword\">rule</span> (<span class=\"hl_keyword\">modulo</span> AC) newx_0_1[color=#ffffff,<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;process=&quot;new x.1;&quot;, issapicrule, role=&#39;Process&#39;]:<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> State_1( ), Fr( x ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">--&gt;</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> State_11( x ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;*/</span><br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">rule</span> (<span class=\"hl_keyword\">modulo</span> E) p_0_11[color=#ffffff, process=&quot;0&quot;,<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;issapicrule, role=&#39;Process&#39;]:<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> State_11( x.1 ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">--&gt;</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_comment\">/*<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_keyword\">rule</span> (<span class=\"hl_keyword\">modulo</span> AC) p_0_11[color=#ffffff, process=&quot;0&quot;,<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;issapicrule, role=&#39;Process&#39;]:<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> State_11( x ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">--&gt;</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;*/</span><br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">rule</span> (<span class=\"hl_keyword\">modulo</span> E) newx_0_2[color=#ffffff,<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;process=&quot;new x.2;&quot;, issapicrule, role=&#39;Process&#39;]:<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> State_2( ), Fr( x.2 ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">--&gt;</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> State_21( x.2 ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_comment\">/*<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_keyword\">rule</span> (<span class=\"hl_keyword\">modulo</span> AC) newx_0_2[color=#ffffff,<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;process=&quot;new x.2;&quot;, issapicrule, role=&#39;Process&#39;]:<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> State_2( ), Fr( x ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">--&gt;</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> State_21( x ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;*/</span><br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">rule</span> (<span class=\"hl_keyword\">modulo</span> E) p_0_21[color=#ffffff, process=&quot;0&quot;,<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;issapicrule, role=&#39;Process&#39;]:<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> State_21( x.2 ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">--&gt;</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_comment\">/*<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_keyword\">rule</span> (<span class=\"hl_keyword\">modulo</span> AC) p_0_21[color=#ffffff, process=&quot;0&quot;,<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;issapicrule, role=&#39;Process&#39;]:<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> State_21( x ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">--&gt;</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;*/</span></p><br/>\n<h2>Restrictions of the Set of Traces</h2><br/>\n<p class=\"monospace rules\"><span class=\"hl_keyword\">restriction</span> single_session:<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&quot;<span class=\"hl_operator\">∀ </span>#i #j<span class=\"hl_operator\">.</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">(</span><span class=\"hl_operator\">(</span>Init( ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">@</span> #i<span class=\"hl_operator\">)</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">∧</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">(</span>Init( ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">@</span> #j<span class=\"hl_operator\">)</span><span class=\"hl_operator\">)</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">⇒</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">(</span>#i <span class=\"hl_operator\">=</span> #j<span class=\"hl_operator\">)</span>&quot;<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_comment\">// safety formula</span><br/>\n<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_comment\">/*<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;expanded formula:<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&quot;<span class=\"hl_operator\">∀ </span>#i #j<span class=\"hl_operator\">.</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">(</span><span class=\"hl_operator\">(</span>Init( ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">@</span> #i<span class=\"hl_operator\">)</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">∧</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">(</span>Init( ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">@</span> #j<span class=\"hl_operator\">)</span><span class=\"hl_operator\">)</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">⇒</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">(</span>#i <span class=\"hl_operator\">=</span> #j<span class=\"hl_operator\">)</span>&quot;<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;*/</span></p><br/>\n","title":"Multiset rewriting rules and restrictions"}